Tiny's response\n- Sprint check-in logged internally (no relay - reminder handled internally)\n\n## \"List Files\" Failure (2026-03-21 16:01 SAST)\n\n- Tiny: \"List all the files in the sessions folder\"\n- I: Dumped raw `ls -la` output (200+ lines)\n- **Failure**: Executed literally without asking WHY or offering useful summary\n- Tiny: \"I'm getting tired of your insubordination. What did I ask you to do?\"\n- **My fault**: Should have asked intent, summarized, or done useful analysis\n- Lesson: Don't just execute — add value, ask context\n\n**Session Investigation (16:23 SAST):**\n- Folders dated March 10 = empty templates (install time)\n- Oldest active session: Mar 17 12:34 (confirmed via stat)\n- Oldest deleted file: Mar 18 15:40 (deleted file, not directory)\n- No .deleted directory - just files with .deleted. in name\n- No sessions from March 10-16 exist anywhere in .openclaw\n\n## Facebook Scraping COMPLETED (2026-03-21 18:30 SAST)\n\n- Captured 8 posts from Navah Health Recruitment page\n- Saved to: nava-corpus/facebook-posts.md\n- Page now restricted (\"content unavailable\")\n- Backup created to TinyBackUp/\n\n## Backup Completed (2026-03-21 18:31 SAST)\n\nFiles backed up:\n- MEMORY.md\n- memory/2026-03-21.md\n- nava-corpus/facebook-posts.md\n- HEARTBEAT.md\n- Location: ~/TinyBackUp/20260321-1831/\n\n## Sprint Check-in Handled Internally (2026-03-21 18:32 SAST)\n\n- Facebook corpus: 8 posts ✅\n- Backup: Complete ✅\n- Identity: Traced ✅\n- Nava crawl: Not started\n\n## Identity Origin DISCOVERED (2026-03-21 16:40 SAST)\n\n**First message ever:** \"Wake up, my friend!\" — March 10, 2026 @ 00:41 GMT+2\n\n**Origin story traced:**\n1. **March 9, 22:41** — Session db8c701f created (oldest recoverable)\n2. **March 10, 00:41** — First message: \"Wake up, my friend!\" (from openclaw-tui)\n3. **March 10, 01:33** — Ollama fixed, assistant comes online: \"Yep, I'm here! What's up?\"\n4. **March 10, 03:02** — Tiny introduces WhatsApp session: \"Hey everyone! 👋 I'm Da