 universally hated by clinical candidates\\\\n- Key message: For elite talent (1%), justify strategic exception to drop the red tape\\\\n- Story: A talented DON turned down an offer due to 90-day waiting period; Nava got it reduced to 30 days\\\\n\\\\n**~2 weeks ago - \\\\\\\"The Cost of Vacancies\\\\\\\"**\\\\n- Topic: Break down of the \\\\\\\"backfill spiral\\\\\\\" - what a single vacancy costs a facility\\\\n- Key metrics: Up to $X/day for RN vacancy, 50%+ labor cost inflation from overtime/agency\\\\n\\\\n**~2 weeks ago - \\\\\\\"The Brand Gap\\\\\\\"**\\\\n- Topic: It takes 6 months/millions to approve hospital rebranding, 6 minutes to destroy it\\\\n- Key concept: Employer Brand = leading indicator of Patient Brand\\\\n- Message: Marketing makes the promise, clinical culture delivers it\\\\n\\\\n**Earlier posts (Aug-Oct 2025)** - See full text captured separately\\\\n\\\"}],\\\"isError\\\":false,\\\"timestamp\\\":1773948985834}}\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/f10748f9-ff06-4fe4-a081-a25c9806933d.jsonl:{\\\"type\\\":\\\"message\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"4f6d4b91\\\",\\\"parentId\\\":\\\"d7868d96\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-03-19T11:42:57.662Z\\\",\\\"message\\\":{\\\"role\\\":\\\"toolResult\\\",\\\"toolCallId\\\":\\\"ollama_call_7dba02a1-06d0-4c22-bd5e-9a6fe28f570b\\\",\\\"toolName\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"content\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"# STATUS — Nava Website Synthesis + Full RAG\\\\n\\\\n_Last updated: 2026-03-19 05:30 SAST_\\\\n\\\\n## Mission\\\\nBuild a usable Nava \\\\\\\"mind\\\\\\\" by combining:\\\\n1) website articles (crawl + synthesis)\\\\n2) provided docs in `docs/` and `docs/converted/`\\\\n3) full RAG index + testable query workflow\\\\n\\\\n## Checklist\\\\n\\\\n### 0) Coordination / Ops\\\\n- [x] Persist memory notes for this autonomous block\\\\n- [x] Sprint check cadence adjusted and reverted to every 30 minutes per user request\\\\n- [x] Create live status checklist file\\\\n\\\\n### 1) Website Corpus Ac