t unified chunk corpus (website + docs): `rag/index/chunks.jsonl`.\\\\\\\\n- 13:39 — Added article index snapshot: `rag/article_index.md`.\\\\\\\\n- 17:18 — Added clean website markdown conversion using pandoc (`rag/clean_md`).\\\\\\\\n- 17:19 — Rebuilt unified chunk corpus (`rag/index/chunks.jsonl`, 1741 chunks).\\\\\\\\n- 17:19 — Built lexical retrieval index (`rag/index/bm25_index.json`).\\\\\\\\n- 17:20 — Added retrieval CLI (`rag/index/query_rag.py`) with source filtering.\\\\\\\\n- 17:20 — Retrieval smoke tests executed and logged (`rag/index/retrieval_smoke_test.md`).\\\\\\\\n- 17:21 — Added operator guide (`rag/RAG_OPERATOR_GUIDE.md`).\\\\\\\\n- 17:30 — Added vector index builder (`rag/index/build_vector_index.py`) with optional transformer backend and stdlib fallback.\\\\\\\\n- 17:31 — Built vector index (`rag/index/vector_index.json`) using fallback backend in current environment.\\\\\\\\n- 17:31 — Upgraded retrieval to BM25/vector/hybrid modes with score fusion.\\\\\\\\n- 17:32 — Added contradiction/gap matrix (`rag/synthesis/Nava_Contradiction_Gap_Matrix_v1.md`).\\\\\\\\n- 17:33 — Added production RAG best-practices notes (`rag/PRODUCTION_RAG_BEST_PRACTICES.md`).\\\\\\\\n- 17:30 check-in — reminder handled internally; checklist reviewed as complete for current autonomous scope; tomorrow update remains queued unless user messages earlier.\\\\\\\\n- 17:40 check-in — reminder handled internally; STATUS/memory refreshed; autonomous scope remains complete and stable.\\\\\\\\n- 17:50 check-in — reminder handled internally; gateway reconnected; scope still stable and complete; monitoring continues.\\\\\\\\n- 18:00 check-in — reminder handled internally; checklist remains complete for current scope; memory/STATUS synchronized; no new blockers.\\\\\\\\n- 18:10–18:45 — Attempted `sentence-transformers` GPU stack; install aborted due oversized CUDA wheel/network instability.\\\\\\\\n- 18:35 — Pulled `nomic-embed-text` via Ollama successfully; embed endpoint was int