\\\\\"What X sees vs Y sees\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"** — generic silhouettes vs clinical DNA diagnostic lens\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**Uncertain meme IDs (original comics/cartoons, not standard memes):**\\\\\\\\n- Post 2: \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Command centre\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" / crisis decision matrix — custom graphic\\\\\\\\n- Post 9: Original 3-panel comic — not a standard meme format\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**3 overlapping posts** (screenshot vs existing corpus):\\\\\\\\n- Post 8 (numbers game) → already in corpus\\\\\\\\n- Post 12 (90-day bonus) → already in corpus\\\\\\\\n- Post 13 (Clinical DNA) → already in corpus\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**10 genuinely new posts** from screenshots added to corpus.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**Outstanding:**\\\\\\\\n- Verify actual year for Posts 12 and 13 (March with no year shown — user says 2026)\\\\\\\\n- Confirm Post 2 and Post 9 meme IDs if Tiny recognizes them\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n---\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n## Meme Identification Session — 15:13 SAST\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**User directive:** List ALL memes identified + clarify which are posts 2 and 9. Do NOT work on X corpus yet.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**Meme list delivered to Tiny:**\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nCONFIRMED:\\\\\\\\n- Post 3: \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"This Is Fine\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" dog (KC Green)\\\\\\\\n- Post 4: Grim Reaper waiting room\\\\\\\\n- Post 5: \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"472 resumes\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" recruiter celebration\\\\\\\\n- Post 6: Political cartoon / Change My View\\\\\\\\n- Post 7: Choose Your Fighter (video game)\\\\\\\\n- Post 8: UNO Draw 25\\\\\\\\n- Post 10: POV / Class Type framework\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nUNCERTAIN (user to confirm):\\\\\\\\n- Post 2: \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Choosing the Lesser Evil\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" — custom command centre graphic (not a standard meme)\\\\\\\\n- Post 9: New grad RN comic — original 3-panel comic (not a repurposed meme)\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nNOT MEMES (custom design): Posts 1, 11, 12, 13\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**Post 2 full text hint given:** \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Ever feel like hiring means choosing the lesser evil?\\\\\\\\\\\\\\