0260320, 20260321, 20260322, etc.)\n- Pattern: `~/TinyBackUp/YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS/` for timestamped snapshots\n\n### Key Files","path":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":44120,"output":811,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44931,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1774272231118}}
