{"type":"message","id":"c54b9406","parentId":"8a9af34b","timestamp":"2026-03-23T13:26:56.922Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"From the skills table in MEMORY.md:\n\n**npm-global skills:**\n| Skill | What it does |\n|---|---|\n| **clawhub** | Search, install, update, publish agent skills from clawhub.com |\n| **healthcheck** | Security audits, SSH/firewall hardening, exposure reviews, OpenClaw version checks |\n| **mcporter** | Connect to MCP servers — Linear, GitHub, Slack, any MCP-compatible tool |\n| **node-connect** | Fix device pairing failures, Tailscale issues, gateway remote URL problems |\n| **session-logs** | Search/analyze session JSONL files using jq patterns |\n| **skill-creator** | Create, edit, audit, or tidy up AgentSkills and SKILL.md files |\n| **tmux** | Remote-control tmux sessions — send keystrokes, scrape pane output |\n| **weather** | Current conditions and forecasts via wttr.in or Open-Meteo |\n\n**Workspace skills:**\n| Skill | What it does |\n|---|---|\n| **linkedin-writer** | Write LinkedIn posts in Tiny's voice — follows his writing style rules |\n| **win-mouse-native** | Move, click, drag the Windows mouse via user32.dll |\n| **visible-browser** | Control WSL Chromium on Tiny's Windows desktop via CDP (port 18801) |\n\n**Other tools I use directly:**\n| Tool | What it does |\n|---|---|\n| **read/write/edit/exec** | File operations and shell commands |\n| **web_search/web_fetch** | Brave search and URL content extraction |\n| **cron** | Schedule reminders and recurring tasks |\n| **memory_search/memory_get** | Query MEMORY.md and daily memory files |\n| **sessions_history/sessions_list** | Read conversation history from session files |\n| **sessions_spawn** | Spawn isolated sub-agents or ACP coding sessions |\n\nAnything you want me to dig into?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":48406,"output":445,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens