e. This resource hub is where we unpack the real stories, strategies, and shifts happening in the way healthcare organizations find and connect with the right people. \n\n## Ready to hire?\n\n Whether you need help with floor staff, leadership roles, or anyone else, we’re ready to find them for you.\n\n Are you a healthcare professional looking for your next opportunity? Click [here](https://navahc.com/candidates/) to submit your resume.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"96aecd76891a496d\">>>"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774272617173}}
